data.description: Welcome home! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5 bath house offers the perfect blend of comfort and elegance. Nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac on a large lot adorned with lush fruit trees (plum, pear, elderberry and blueberry) this property offers ample space to relax, entertain, and spread out. The upstairs loft area is a versatile space that can be used as a home office, playroom, or additional living area. Perfectly situated close to shopping centers and a variety of restaurant. Tour this home today!
